# Include your project-specific ignores in this file
# Read about how to use .gitignore: https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files

# --- Go ---
/safu                 # built binary (go build ./cmd/safu)
safu                  # built binary, anywhere
/dist-bin/            # local cross-compile output
*.exe
*.exe~
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib
*.test                # test binaries (go test -c)
*.out                 # profiling / coverage output
coverage.*
*.prof
go.work
go.work.sum
vendor/

# --- Website (site/) ---
site/node_modules/
site/dist/
node_modules
dist
.cache

# --- Editors / IDEs ---
.idea/
*.iml
.vscode/
*.swp
*.swo
*~

# --- Markdown docs (excluded for now; add explicitly with `git add -f <file>.md`) ---
*.md

# --- OS ---
.DS_Store
.DS_Store?
._*
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
